# Keep build contexts lean and avoid leaking local state into images.
# Dev compose bind-mounts source on top of the image, so build context only
# needs package manifests + lockfiles + the seed source.

**/node_modules
**/dist
**/build
**/.vite
**/*.tsbuildinfo

# Python
**/__pycache__
**/.venv
**/venv
**/*.pyc
**/.pytest_cache
**/.ruff_cache
**/.mypy_cache

# Env / secrets
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example

# VCS / CI / docs
.git
.github
**/*.md
docs

# Test / coverage artifacts
**/coverage
**/playwright-report
**/test-results

# Editor / OS
**/.vscode
**/.idea
**/.DS_Store
*.log
